data.description: HOME ON 2 ACRES!! Beautiful wooden, vaulted ceiling in living room featuring wood-burning stove. Formal Dining room with built-in buffet. Spacious kitchen with island, built in office nook, plenty of cabinetry for storage, plus area for additional dining. Small bonus room to be used as large pantry or office space. Huge bonus room or 4TH bedroom accessible by spiral staircase. Large covered porch off of dining room. Outdoor storage buildings. Peaceful and convenient!
